    "title": "驾考新政实施在即 驾考难度或将增加",
    "time": "2017/8/15",
    "content": "<span id='LabelHtmlContent'><div class='rich_media_content ' id='js_content' style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); position: relative; min-height: 350px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; white-space: normal;'><section class='' data-id='29735' style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;'><section style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 92px; word-wrap: break-word !important;'><p style='margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: center; color: inherit; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word !important;'><span style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-color: rgb(226, 121, 97); color: rgb(226, 121, 97); word-wrap: break-word !important;'><strong style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-color: rgb(226, 121, 97); color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important;'>驾考那点事</strong></span></p></section><section style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px 5px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 10px; color: inherit; border: 1px solid rgb(226, 121, 97); word-wrap: break-word !important;'><section data-width='50%' style='margin: -8px 0px 0px 140px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: inherit; height: 8px; width: 329px; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: #f5f5f5;'><section style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; font-size: 18px; text-decoration: inherit; border-color: rgb(226, 121, 97); display: inline-block; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(226, 121, 97);'></section></section><section class='' data-style='text-indent: 2em;' style='margin: 15px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 2em; font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word !important;'><span style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word !important;'>近期，交管局出台了一系列驾考新规，提高驾照考试难度、建立考试发证和执法管理责任倒查制度都名列其中，使得考驾照与学员今后的驾驶道路产生了紧密的联系，从今以后，学车难度真的要加大了。</span></section><section data-width='65%' style='margin: 0px 0px -4px 25px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: inherit; text-align: right; height: 10px; width: 427.688px; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: #f5f5f5;'><section style='margin: 0px auto 1px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border-radius: 100%; line-height: 1; text-decoration: inherit; border-color: rgb(226, 121, 97); display: inline-block; height: 8px; width: 8px; color: inherit; word-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(226, 121, 97);'></section></section></section></section><p style='margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;'><span style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; word-wrap: break-word !important;'>&nbsp;</span></p><section class='' data-id='1' style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;'><h2 class='' placeholder='请输入标题' style='margin: 10px 0px; padding: 5px 10px; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-left-width: 5px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(102, 103, 101); line-height: 32px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); word-wrap: break-word !important;'>政策丨驾驶人发生事故将倒查考试员</h2></section><p style='margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word !important;'><br style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;'></p><p style='margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;'><span style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; word-wrap: break-word !important;'>该项政策规定：驾驶人拿证3年内发生交通死亡事故将倒查考试员。也就是说，学员拿证以后不仅没有万事大吉，相反，拿证后的驾驶行为也将与驾校挂钩，<span style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;'>考试标准是否严格，考试内容是否适用于具体情况</span>，这些都是未来要考虑的方向。</span></p><p style='margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;'><span style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; word-wrap: break-word !important;'>&nbsp;</span></p><section class='' data-id='1' style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; border: 0px none; word-wrap: break-word !important;'><h2 class='' placeholder='请输入标题' style='margin: 10px 0px; padding: 5px 10px; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; border-left-width: 5px; border-left-style: solid; border-left-color: rgb(102, 103, 101); line-height: 32px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); word-wrap: break-word !important;'>倒查制度迫使考试难度增加</h2></section><p style='margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word !important;'><br style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important;'></p><p style='margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;'><span style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; word-wrap: break-word !important;'>现阶段的驾考难度可能仅仅停留在应试阶段，实用性少。大部分考生通过考试除了技术以外，运气也占很大成分。在考试制度下、考官面前你可能通过了，但是不一定能过实际道路操作这关，这也在一定程度上增加了开车上路的风险。</span></p><p style='margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;'><span style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; word-wrap: break-word !important;'>&nbsp;</span></p><p style='margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; word-wrap: break-word !important;'><span style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; word-wrap: break-word !important;'>以往学员在科目三训练时都是在空旷路段，缺乏对突发情况的应变能力。<span style='margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(0, 82, 255); word-wrap: break-word !important;'>新规提出后，将以提高考生对恶劣天气、复杂路况和突然情况的能力为主。总之，为了学员的安全考虑，今后的考试或许将更加注重开车的实用性。学车越来越难了。</span></span></p></div><div class='rich_media_tool' id='js_toobar3' style='margin: 0px; padding: 15px 0px 0px; font-size: 14px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 32px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif; white-space: normal;'></div><p><br></p></span>"
  },
